WEBVTT

00:01.075 --> 00:02.860
Previously on
<i>Camelot...</i>

00:02.895 --> 00:04.610
You're not welcome, Morgan.

00:04.645 --> 00:07.925
Father, I learned more
than you can imagine.

00:08.235 --> 00:10.625
Uther! Somebody help him!

00:10.660 --> 00:12.050
<i>Merlin!</i>

00:12.085 --> 00:14.675
<i>The King is dead. Murdered.</i>

00:14.710 --> 00:15.995
What's that got to do with us?

00:16.030 --> 00:18.770
You... are Uther's son.

00:18.805 --> 00:20.900
I'm Uther's
daughter and sole heir.

00:20.935 --> 00:26.365
If we forge a union, we'd have
the strength to unite the realm.

00:26.505 --> 00:29.355
Who is she? Who is she?

00:29.390 --> 00:30.620
I don't know!

00:30.655 --> 00:33.575
I am the true and legitimate
heir to Uther's throne.

00:33.610 --> 00:35.555
And you will show me respect!

00:35.590 --> 00:37.685
No!

00:37.935 --> 00:42.375
But if you don't leave,
there will be more slaughter.

00:42.400 --> 00:46.400
